  2015,"10",/general-conference/2015/10/the-sustaining-of-church-officers,"",10,"Los que estén en contra, pueden indicarlo."
  2015,"10",/general-conference/2015/10/the-sustaining-of-church-officers,"",11,El voto ha sido registrado.
  2015,"10",/general-conference/2015/10/the-sustaining-of-church-officers,"",12,"Se propone que sostengamos a los consejeros de la Primera Presidencia y al Cuórum de los Doce Apóstoles como profetas, videntes y reveladores."
  2015,"10",/general-conference/2015/10/the-sustaining-of-church-officers,"",13,"Todos los que estén a favor, sírvanse manifestarlo."
